          ## Implementation Process

          ### Phase 1: Discovery and Planning (2 months)
          - Comprehensive analysis of existing risk assessment workflows
          - Stakeholder interviews with risk analysts and compliance officers
          - Data audit and quality assessment
          - Technical architecture design and approval

          ### Phase 2: Development and Training (4 months)
          - Data pipeline development and testing
          - LLM fine-tuning and validation
          - Dashboard and user interface development
          - Integration with existing systems

          ### Phase 3: Pilot Testing (2 months)
          - Limited deployment with select risk assessment teams
          - Performance monitoring and optimization
          - User feedback collection and incorporation
          - Accuracy validation against manual assessments

          ### Phase 4: Full Deployment (1 month)
          - Organization-wide rollout
          - User training and support
          - Performance monitoring and optimization
